paragraphs.title: APP被扫
paragraphs.text:
select trim(app_ins_id_cd),count(*) as cnt,count(case when up_discount>0 then 1 else null end) as dis from
upw_hive.view_glhis_qrhis_trans_flow
where substr(order_type,1,2)='01'
and trim(trans_tp) in ('01','04','31')
and hp_settle_dt between  regexp_replace(date_add(current_date,-7),'-','') and regexp_replace(date_add(current_date,-1),'-','')
group by trim(app_ins_id_cd)
order by cnt desc

paragraphs.title: 场景交易情况
paragraphs.text:
--%impalajdbc
select substr(dt,1,6) as month,
(case 
when scene_nm1 in ('自助售货','自助售货机') then '自助售货'
when scene_nm1='菜场及生活圈' then '菜场及生活圈' 
when scene_nm1 in ('高校') then '高校'
when scene_nm1='食堂' then '食堂'
when MCC in ('4111','4121','4131','4874','4523')  and substr(order_type,1,2)='01' then '公交地铁类'
when MCC in ('5611','5621','5631','5641','5651','5655','5661','5681','5691','5698','5699','5713','5714','5719','5948','5949','5977','5997','7278','5211','5231','5251','5261','5309','5310','5311','5712','5718','5732','5931','5940','5941','5942','5943','5945','5947','5973','5983','5992','5999','8043','5399','4812','5733','5735','5946','5411','5972','9706','5541','5542','5331') and (substr(order_type,1,2)='01' or trim(order_type) in ('0210','0211')) then '商超便利类'
when MCC in ('5811','5812','5813','5814') and (substr(order_type,1,2)='01' or trim(order_type) in ('0210','0211')) then '餐饮类' 
when trim(order_type) in ('0212','0214','0215') then '小微' 
else '其他' end) as scene,count(*) as cnt,count(distinct user_id),sum(trans_at)/100 from
(
select hp_settle_dt as dt,scene_nm1,substr(c.mchnt_cd,8,4) as MCC,mchnt_usr_id as user_id,order_type,trans_at
from upw_hive.view_glhis_qrhis_trans_flow c
left join 
(
select scene_nm1,mchnt_cd from 
upw_hive.hv_rtapam_dim_scene_base_inf 
where trim(scene_nm1) in ('自助售货','自助售货机','菜场及生活圈','高校','食堂')
) as d
on trim(c.mchnt_cd)=(d.mchnt_cd)
where (substr(order_type,1,2)='01' or trim(order_type) in ('0210','0211','0212','0214','0215'))
and trim(trans_tp)='01' 
and trim(proc_st)='00' 
and trim(resp_cd)='0000000'
and hp_settle_dt between  regexp_replace(date_add(current_date,-7),'-','') and regexp_replace(date_add(current_date,-1),'-','')
and trim(app_ins_id_cd) ='00250001' 
) aa
group by substr(dt,1,6),
(case 
when scene_nm1 in ('自助售货','自助售货机') then '自助售货'
when scene_nm1='菜场及生活圈' then '菜场及生活圈' 
when scene_nm1 in('高校') then '高校'  
when scene_nm1='食堂' then '食堂'
when MCC in ('4111','4121','4131','4874','4523')  and substr(order_type,1,2)='01' then '公交地铁类'
when MCC in ('5611','5621','5631','5641','5651','5655','5661','5681','5691','5698','5699','5713','5714','5719','5948','5949','5977','5997','7278','5211','5231','5251','5261','5309','5310','5311','5712','5718','5732','5931','5940','5941','5942','5943','5945','5947','5973','5983','5992','5999','8043','5399','4812','5733','5735','5946','5411','5972','9706','5541','5542','5331') and (substr(order_type,1,2)='01' or trim(order_type) in ('0210','0211')) then '商超便利类'
when MCC in ('5811','5812','5813','5814') and (substr(order_type,1,2)='01' or trim(order_type) in ('0210','0211')) then '餐饮类' 
when trim(order_type) in ('0212','0214','0215') then '小微' 
else '其他' end)

paragraphs.title: 公交TOP20
paragraphs.text:
select 
--hp_settle_dt,
(case  when branch is null then '其他' else branch end) as pro,
count(case when substr(a.mchnt_cd,8,4) in ('4111','4121','4411','4131','4874','4523') then 1 else null end) as `交易笔数`,
count(case when substr(a.mchnt_cd,8,4) in ('4111','4121','4411','4131','4874','4523') and up_discount>0 then 1 else null end) as `优惠笔数`,
count(case when substr(a.mchnt_cd,8,4) in ('4111','4121','4411','4131','4874','4523') and trans_at>300 then 1 else null end) as `3元以上金额`
from 
upw_hive.view_glhis_qrhis_trans_flow a
left join 
(
select region_cd,city,branch from upw_hive.tmj_branch_cd 
) b 
on a.area_cd=b.region_cd 
where substr(a.order_type,1,2)='01'
and trim(trans_tp) ='01'
--and a.pri_acct_no not like '62135101000723%' 
and trim(a.app_ins_id_cd) ='00250001'
and trim(a.proc_st)='00' 
and trim(a.resp_cd)='0000000'
and a.hp_settle_dt between regexp_replace(date_add(current_date,-7),'-','') and regexp_replace(date_add(current_date,-1),'-','')
group by 
--hp_settle_dt,
(case  when branch is null then '其他' else branch end)
order by `交易笔数` desc

paragraphs.title: 被扫分公司
paragraphs.text:
select (case  when branch is null then '其他' else branch end) as pro,
sum(a.cnt) as `交易笔数`,
sum(a.jine) as `交易金额`,
sum(a.cnt1) as `成功交易笔数`, 
sum(a.trans) as `成功交易金额`,
sum(a.cnt2) as `支付成功交易笔数`, 
sum(a.pays) as `支付成功交易金额`, 
sum(a.cnt4) as `优惠成功交易笔数`,
sum(a.dis) as `优惠成功交易金额`
 from  
(
select area_cd,
count(case when trim(trans_tp) in ('01','04','31')  then 1 else null end) as cnt,
sum(case when trim(trans_tp) in ('01','04','31') then trans_at else 0 end) / 100 as jine,
count(case when trim(trans_tp) in ('01','04','31') and trim(resp_cd) in ('0000000','6820000')  then 1 else null end) as cnt1,
count(case when trim(trans_tp) in ('01') and trim(resp_cd) in ('0000000') then 1 else null end) as cnt2,
sum(case when trim(trans_tp) in ('01','04','31') and trim(resp_cd) in ('0000000','6820000')  then trans_at else 0 end) / 100 as trans,
sum(case when trim(trans_tp) in ('01') and trim(resp_cd) in ('0000000')  then trans_at else 0 end) / 100 as pays,
count(case when trim(trans_tp)='01' and trim(resp_cd)='0000000' and trim(proc_st)='00' and up_discount>0  then 1 else null end) as cnt4,
sum(case when trim(trans_tp)='01' and trim(resp_cd)='0000000' and trim(proc_st)='00' and up_discount>0  then up_discount else 0 end) / 100 as dis  
from 
upw_hive.view_glhis_qrhis_trans_flow
where substr(order_type,1,2)='01'  
and trim(app_ins_id_cd) ='00250001' 
and hp_settle_dt between regexp_replace(date_add(current_date,-7),'-','') and regexp_replace(date_add(current_date,-1),'-','')
group by area_cd
) a 
left join 
(
select region_cd,city,branch from upw_hive.tmj_branch_cd 
) b 
on a.area_cd=b.region_cd 
group by (case  when branch is null then '其他' else branch end)
order by `交易笔数` desc

paragraphs.title: 主扫新增用户构成
paragraphs.text:
--%impalajdbc
select count(distinct  new.cdhd_usr_id) as `注册用户数`,
count(distinct if(b.activity_id in ('994','995','998','1003','1005','1016')  and e.org_code is null,b.cdhd_usr_id ,null)) as `机构激励`,
count(distinct if(b.activity_id in  ('996','1000','1007','1009','1013','1015','1020','1022','1023','1025','1026','1028','1030','1032','1037','1039','1048','1050','1051','1064','1066')  ,b.cdhd_usr_id , null)) as `老带新`,
count(distinct if(b.activity_id in ('997','1001','1008','1010','1014','1021','1024','1027','1031','1038','1040','1047','1049','1065') or (e.org_code is not null and activity_id in ('994','995','998','1003','1005','1016')),b.cdhd_usr_id ,null)) as `三覆盖`,
count(distinct if(b.cdhd_usr_id is null,new.cdhd_usr_id,null)) as `自主注册`
from
(
select distinct cdhd_usr_id from 
upw_hive.view_chacc_cdhd_pri_acct_inf
where usr_st='1'
--and trim(inf_source)<>'merchant'
and part_dt between date_add(current_date,-7) and date_add(current_date,-1)
) new
inner join 
(
select mchnt_usr_id as cdhd_usr_id from
upw_hive.view_glhis_qrhis_trans_flow
where trim(order_type) in ('0210','0211','0212','0214','0215')
and trim(trans_tp)='01' 
and trim(resp_cd)='0000000' 
and trim(proc_st)='00' 
and hp_settle_dt between regexp_replace(date_add(current_date,-7),'-','') and regexp_replace(date_add(current_date,-1),'-','')
and trim(app_ins_id_cd) ='00250001'
) c
on new.cdhd_usr_id=c.cdhd_usr_id
left join 
(
select  cdhd_usr_id,activity_id,institution_id 
from upw_hive.view_chmkt_recmd_inf
where user_st in ('01','02','03','04','91','92','93') 
and award_user_st='2'
) b
on new.cdhd_usr_id=b.cdhd_usr_id  
left join
(select org_code from hv_tbl_m2vop_org_info where sec_org_type='04')e
on b.institution_id=e.org_code

paragraphs.title: 新增主扫用户（按日）

--%impalajdbc
select hp_settle_dt,count(distinct a.mchnt_usr_id) from 
(
select distinct mchnt_usr_id,hp_settle_dt from
upw_hive.view_glhis_qrhis_trans_flow

and trim(app_ins_id_cd) ='00250001' 
and hp_settle_dt between regexp_replace(date_add(current_date,-7),'-','') and regexp_replace(date_add(current_date,-1),'-','')

and trim(proc_st)='00' 
) a

(

upw_hive.view_chacc_cdhd_pri_acct_inf
